Author: Neil H
Subject: I'd love to keep an archive of older events
Body: Or the ability to dump my started content etc to xml/Google drive or whatever before the next schedule is released. I was using starred events to know what videos from the archive I wanted to watch. The app app is great, and really helps plan your route at the event. Thanks as ever, especially for responding to feedback.

Author: Matthew Copperwaite
Subject: Much better than the schedule app
Body: I had a little difficulty downloading the schedule at first but this fixes all of the problems I had with the other schedule app. You can now see what's coming up really easily and set how long before the event you want to be notified. Great work.

Author: aleta dunne
Subject: Fantastic app!
Body: This app is very easy to use; better than many conference apps I've tried. The notifications for upcoming sessions I've starred can be turned off or changed in the settings, and I appreciated the links to a map of the session location for each session so I can find my way there quickly.  The only improvement I can think of is to make it easier to find the next sessions as the  conference goes on; right now when I go to the list of sessions I starred, or a list of all the sessions in a specific track, it lists them chronologically and as the conference goes on, I have to check the current time and scroll to the appropriate place in the list.  I would love it if it jumped past or greyed out the sessions that are over so that I can more easily identify current & future sessions.  Thank you Christophe!
